sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor User as User (Browser)
    participant Web as Web Dashboard (React)
    participant API as Backend API (Render)
    participant DB as Supabase (DB)
    participant Q as Redis Queue (Upstash)
    participant Worker as Worker Node (Local/Cloud)
    participant Git as GitHub

    User->>Web: Pastes GitHub URL and clicks Scan

    Note over Web,API: POST /api/scans/github
    Web->>API: Sends github_url payload

    API->>DB: Creates Scan Record Status PENDING
    API->>Q: Pushes Job Ticket to Queue Includes URL
    API-->>Web: Returns 202 Accepted plus scan_id

    loop Every 5 Seconds
        Note over Web,API: GET /api/scans/{scan_id}
        Web->>API: Check scan status
        API-->>Web: Status SCANNING
    end

    Q->>Worker: Pulls Job Ticket

    Note right of Worker: The difference happens here
    Worker->>Git: Executes git clone github_url
    Git-->>Worker: Downloads source code directly to Worker

    Note right of Worker: Runs Scan Engine and LangGraph Agents

    Worker->>API: Webhook POST Final Verified Bugs
    API->>DB: Updates Status to COMPLETED and Saves Data

    Web->>API: Check scan status
    API-->>Web: Status COMPLETED with Bug List Payload
    Web->>User: Renders Vulnerability Dashboard